Package pl.edu.wsisiz.darkavenger54

Class Group

  • java.lang.Object
    • pl.edu.wsisiz.darkavenger54.Group
  • public class Group
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a student group with a specific ID, specialization, and description. It contains a list of students that belong to the group.
